		<SectionContainer class="py-44 pb-32">

			<h1 class="text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold flex flex-row gap-x-4 pb-6 lg:pb-10">Hey, I'm Joaquin Herrera <div class="flex justify-center items-center"><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/joaquin-herrera-396150183" target="_blank"><Badge>Open to work</Badge></a> </div></h1>
